Class RenderClique

  • java.lang.Object
    • tracer.renders.Render
      • tracer.renders.RenderClique
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    processing.core.PConstants, Drawable

    public class RenderClique
extends Render
    Draws a list of Tracers as a clique (a fully-connected graph), where lines are drawn between each Tracer and every other Tracer
    Author:
    James Morrow [jamesmorrowdesign.com]
